PHP - Sort Functions For Arrays ->

In this chapter, we will go through the following PHP array sort functions:

	1. sort() - sort arrays in ascending order
	2. rsort() - sort arrays in descending order

	3. asort() - sort associative arrays in ascending order, according to the value(associative array)
	4. ksort() - sort associative arrays in ascending order, according to the key(associative array)
	5. arsort() - sort associative arrays in descending order, according to the value(associative array)
	6. krsort() - sort associative arrays in descending order, according to the key(associative array)
